nd":"text","text":"(Jel:) and in the Kur li. 11,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in overwhelming ignorance:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Bd, Jel:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gamorapN","text_ar":"غَمْرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies [here]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a state of obstinate perseverance in vain"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"false affairs:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, Msb, TA:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gamaraAtN","text_ar":"غَمَرَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is the pl. (Msb.) You say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"huwa fiY gamorapK","text_ar":"هُوَ فِى غَمْرَةٍ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mino lahowK","text_ar":"مِنْ لَهْوٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$abiybapK","text_ar":"شَبِيبَةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sukorK","text_ar":"سُكْرٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He is in a submerging gulf,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"flood, of frivolous diversion,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of youthful folly,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of intoxication"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.)"},{"kind":"page_break","n":2293},{"kind":"text","text":"And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gamaraAtu jahan~ama","text_ar":"غَمَرَاتُ جَهَنَّمَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The fiery depths of Hell;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the places, of Hell, that abound with fire."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b3-  [Hence]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gamorapu AlxuSuwmapi","text_ar":"غَمْرَةُ الخُصُومَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The main part of the contention."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) [And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gamorapu","text_ar":"غَمْرَةُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlHarobi","text_ar":"الحَرْبِ"},{"kind"